01:12:27.029 --> 01:12:31.029
Are we going to really be happy from our heart with our brother?

01:12:31.029 --> 01:12:35.029
Well if we love our brother and we love Jehovah,

01:12:35.029 --> 01:12:39.029
then we're going to work really hard to have that right attitude from our heart.

01:12:39.029 --> 01:12:44.029
See, we will smash any hint of jealousy.

01:12:44.029 --> 01:12:47.029
We'll smash it with love.

01:12:47.029 --> 01:12:50.029
Now here's a fifth thing we can do.

01:12:50.029 --> 01:12:55.029
