01:12:55.029 --> 01:12:59.029
such as the elders, and obviously doing that.

01:12:59.029 --> 01:13:06.029
Supporting these ones or taking the lead definitely promotes peace and joy in the congregation.

01:13:06.029 --> 01:13:08.029
Here's one more thing.

01:13:08.029 --> 01:13:13.029
Center your life on serving Jehovah and helping others,

01:13:13.029 --> 01:13:16.029
rather than focusing on ourselves.

01:13:16.029 --> 01:13:19.029
Maybe our feelings,

01:13:19.029 --> 01:13:22.029
our perceived reputation,

01:13:22.029 --> 01:13:25.029
if we focus on serving Jehovah

01:13:25.029 --> 01:13:27.029
and helping our brothers,

01:13:27.029 --> 01:13:31.029
will truly be peace promoters in the congregation.

01:13:31.029 --> 01:13:33.029
By doing those six things,

01:13:33.029 --> 01:13:36.029
we'll prove that we're peacemakers,

01:13:36.029 --> 01:13:40.029
peace promoters who are reflecting the wisdom from above.

