01:18:09.180 --> 01:18:11.180
And now, I am finding real joy

01:18:11.180 --> 01:18:14.180
and satisfaction in my service to Jehovah.

01:18:14.180 --> 01:18:18.010
So may each of us

01:18:18.010 --> 01:18:21.010
prayerfully work to have the attitude

01:18:21.010 --> 01:18:24.010
