01:54:29.579 --> 01:54:31.579
and especially those final hours,

01:54:31.579 --> 01:54:35.579
and then those hours on the torture stake,

01:54:35.579 --> 01:54:37.579
and he knew what was coming,

01:54:37.579 --> 01:54:40.579
the details.

01:54:40.579 --> 01:54:44.579
How does a man deal with that

01:54:44.579 --> 01:54:48.579
without collapsing?

01:54:48.579 --> 01:54:52.579
Well, we're not left to wonder

01:54:52.579 --> 01:54:55.579
for the joy that was said before him,

01:54:55.579 --> 01:54:57.579
hindered all that.

01:54:57.579 --> 01:55:00.579
So Jesus had the prehuman existence,

01:55:00.579 --> 01:55:03.579
the joy of sitting with his father again

01:55:03.579 --> 01:55:06.579
in the heavens, oh, my,

01:55:06.579 --> 01:55:09.579
it got him through it.

01:55:09.579 --> 01:55:11.579
Same for us brothers,

01:55:11.579 --> 01:55:16.149
the joy will get us through it.

01:55:16.149 --> 01:55:19.149
The joy of staying close with our God,

01:55:19.149 --> 01:55:22.149
and finally this last verse

01:55:22.149 --> 01:55:25.149
for this closing talk here,

01:55:25.149 --> 01:55:29.880
Romans chapter 12.

